    <main class="cat-care">
        <section class="care-intro">
            <h2>Cat Care Tips</h2>
            <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
            <p>Cats are independent creatures, but they rely on us for food, shelter, love, and medical care. Here are some tips to help keep your cat healthy and happy.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="care-tips">
            <div class="tip">
                <img src="/Images/nutrition-icon.webp" alt="Nutrition">
                <h3>Nutrition</h3>
                <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
                <p>Feed your cat a balanced diet tailored to its age, health status, and lifestyle.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <img src="/Images/environment-icon.jpg" alt="Environment">
                <h3>Environment</h3>
                <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
                <p>Provide a stimulating and safe environment with scratching posts, toys, and comfortable resting areas.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <img src="/Images/grooming-icon-cat.jpg" alt="Grooming">
                <h3>Grooming</h3>
                <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
                <p>Regular grooming helps keep your cat's coat healthy and reduces shedding. Brush their coat and trim their nails regularly.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <img src="/Images/training-icon-cat.webp" alt="Training">
                <h3>Training</h3>
                <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
                <p>Cats can be trained using positive reinforcement techniques. Start with litter box training and basic commands like come and stay.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tip">
                <img src="/Images/healthcare-icon-cat.jpeg" alt="Healthcare">
                <h3>Healthcare</h3>
                <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
                <p>Regular vet check-ups, vaccinations, and preventive care are essential for your cat's well-being.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="more-info">
            <h2>Further Information</h2>
            <p>For more comprehensive guides on cat care, check out our resources or contact us for advice.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn">Get in Touch</a>
        </section>
    </main>
